data.description: Prime location in a well established Dallas neighborhood within walking distance to parks and schools. This 4 bedroom, 2 and a half bath, 2 living areas and a nice size backyard is perfect for a family. The 2 generous living areas and dining room will be perfect for  holidays. 3 bedrooms have walk-in closets and the primary bedroom has a bonus room that could be used for an office or nursery. Plenty of parking in the oversize garage or in the long driveway may fit up to 8 cars
